songs.title: Amanamaa
songs.lyrics:
Da'oo Gaarii isa duwwaa argeeraa
Hirkoo Gaarii isa duwwaa argeeraa
Michuu Gaarii isa duwwaa argeeraa
Tiksee Gaarii isa duwwaa argeeraa
Amanamaa isa  duwwaa argeeraa*4

Biyyi lafaa Summidhaa Kan dhamdhamni isaa mi'aawuu
Hojjettonni isaa hunduu Osuma kolfanii du'uu
Harka bitaan badhaasee mirgadhaan saama deebisee
Gargaaree gaara baasee achirratti yellasisee
Amanamaa isa duwwaa argeera*4

Jaalalli kee na dhibaa mana kee keessat na eegee
Natti in yayyaadatamaa na keessa hin badu oolmaan kee
Isan barbaadee dhabee barbaadee iddo hundumaatii
Gaarumma guddaan argee abbaa koo anoo si keessatti

Yoomiyyuu dhugaa mitii addunyaan kun gaaddiddudhaa
Iddo ganamaa hin jiruu galgallisaa ilkan qaruudha
Nagaanis hin argamuu karaa kana kan hiyyoomtee
Hamtuudha biyyi lafaa hammeenyan kan badhaadhomtee

Da'oo gaari si duwwaa argeera
Hirkoo gaari si duwwaa argeera
Michuu gaari si duwwaa argeera
Tiksee gaari si duwwaa argeera
Amanamaa isa duwwaa argeera*4
